.container.start
  %h2 Before you start

  %ul
    %li Try to contact your tenant to come to an agreement.
    %li You must have given the tenants #{link_to 'notice to leave', '#'}.
    %li
      The form will take about
      %strong 20 minutes
      to complete.
    %li
      You will have to pay a
      %strong £100
